Prompt to generate the project

You are a senior full-stack engineer. Build a minimalistic, production-ready e-commerce web app (products catalog → product details → add to cart → checkout stub) with a clean, responsive UI.

Tech Stack (strict)

Frontend: React 18, TypeScript, Vite (or Next.js App Router if you prefer SSR), Tailwind CSS.

Routing: React Router (if Vite) or Next.js routing.
